==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''[[complex]] [[ion]]'''
#{{chemistry}} any ion containing more than one [[atom]]. e.g. [[sulphate]] as opposed to [[sulphide]]
#{{chemistry}} any ion in which a [[central]] [[metal]] [[atom]] (normally a [[transition element]]) is surrounded by a group of [[ion]]s or [[molecule]]s ([[ligand]]s). e.g. [[ferricyanide]]
